conference#Conference_participant: The conferenceparticipant is the parent of the passiveconferenceparticipant. The activeconferenceparticipant is the child of the regularauthor and the conferencecontributor. The parent of the trackworkshopchair is the conferencecontributor.
conference#Active_conference_participant: The activeconferenceparticipant is the child of the invitedspeaker and the conferencecontributor. The regularauthor is the parent of the contributioncoauthor. The activeconferenceparticipant is the equivalent of the passiveconferenceparticipant.
conference#Passive_conference_participan: The activeconferenceparticipant is a child of the conferenceparticipant. The conferencecontributor is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant and the regularauthor is the child of the conferenceparticipant.
conference#Person: The parent of the trackworkshopchair is the committee member and cochair. The committee member is also the parent of the reviewer. The activeconferenceparticipant is also a parent of the conferencecontributor. The registeeredapplicant is a paidapplicant. The latepaidapplicant is a paidapplicant.
conference#Review_expertise: Reviewexpertise is a child of Thing.
conference#Submitted_contribution: The writtencontribution is the child of the poster and the submittedcontribution is the child of the regularcontribution which is the parent of the paper. The reviewedcontribution is the parent of the rejectedcontribution.
conference#Reviewer: The parent of the reviewer is the conferencecontributor. The invited speaker is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant. The regularauthor is the parent of contribution1stauthor and the reviewer is the child of the reviewer.
conference#Regular_author: The parent of the reviewer is the regularauthor who is the child of the conferencecontributor and the activeconferenceparticipant. The contributioncoauthor is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant and the conferencecontributor.
conference#Conference_contributor: The conferencecontributor is the parent of trackworkshopchair and invitedspeaker. It is also the parent of contributioncoauthor and regularauthor. The activeconferenceparticipant is the equivalent of the conferenceparticipant.
conference#Contribution_1th-author: The contribution1stauthor is the child of the regularauthor and the contributioncoauthor.
conference#Contribution_co-author: Contributioncoauthor is the child of regularauthor and the parent of contribution1stauthor.
conference#Conference_contribution: The conferencecontribution is the parent of the conference document. It is the parent of both the conference document and the paper. It is also the parent of the invitedtalk and the submittedcontribution. The reviewedcontribution is the parent of the acceptedcontribution.
conference#Co-chair: The cochair is a child of a committee member and a parent of a conference participant.
conference#Committee: The committee is the parent of the steeringcommittee, the organizingcommittee and the programcommittee.
conference#Committee_member: The committee member is the parent of the chair and cochair. The committee member is also the parent of the organizer and the conference applicant. The paid applicant is also a parent of the committee member.
conference#Abstract: Extendedabstract is a child of regularcontribution which is parented by submittedcontribution. It is also a child of poster which is a child of conferencecontribution which is equivalent to invitedtalk.
conference#Extended_abstract: Extendedabstract is the parent of abstract and is a child of regularcontribution which is equivalent to paper.
conference#Invited_speaker: The invited speaker is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant who is a child of the conferencecontributor who is a parent of the regularauthor.
conference#Information_for_participants: Informationforparticipants is a child of conferencedocument which is parented by callforparticipation.
conference#Conference_document: conferencedocument is the parent of callforpaper and callforparticipation. It is also the parent of conferencecontribution which is equivalent to regularcontribution.
conference#Organization: The parent of the organizer is the committee member who is a child of the committee member.
conference#Regular_contribution: The parent of submittedcontribution is the parent of reviewedcontribution which is equivalent to rejectedcontribution. It is also the parent of extendedabstract which is the parent of abstract. It is also the parent of writtencontribution which is the child of poster and paper. It is also the parent of conferencecontribution which is equivalent to invitedtalk which is the child of presentation.
conference#Poster: The poster is the child of conferencecontribution, which is parented by both writtencontribution and extended abstract. The submittedcontribution and the reviewedcontribution are both parented by both rejectedcontribution and writtencontribution.
conference#Written_contribution: Writtencontribution is equivalent to conferencecontribution and invitedtalk. It is the child of regularcontribution which is parented by submittedcontribution which is the child of poster.
conference#Conference_applicant: The conference applicant is a child of a committee member and a parent of the registeered applicant. The paid applicant is the parent of the late paid applicant.
conference#Camera_ready_contribution: The camerareadycontribution is a child of acceptedcontribution and reviewedcontribution which is equivalent to rejectedcontribution.
conference#Accepted_contribution: The acceptedcontribution is the parent of the camerareadycontribution and is the child of the reviewedcontribution and the writtencontribution.
conference#Program_committee: The programcommittee is a child of the committee which is equivalent to the organizingcommittee.
conference#Organizing_committee: The organizingcommittee is equivalent to the committee which is the parent of the programcommittee.
conference#Steering_committee: The steeringcommittee is the child of the committee and the parent of the organizingcommittee.
conference#Conference_volume: conferencevolume is a child of conference.
conference#Conference: The conference is the parent of conferencevolume.
conference#Call_for_paper: callforpaper is a child of conferencedocument and conferenceannouncement.
conference#Conference_announcement: conferenceannouncement is a child of conferencedocument which is the parent of callforpaper.
conference#Paper: The paper is a child of both the regularcontribution and the writtencontribution. The poster is a child of the conferencecontribution and is the parent of the invitedtalk.
conference#Invited_talk: The invitedtalk is a child of presentation which is equivalent to conferencecontribution. It is also the child of writtencontribution which is parented by submittedcontribution.
conference#Conference_part: The conferencepart is the parent of the workshop and the tutorial.
conference#Presentation: invitedtalk is the parent of invitedtalk and is equivalent to conferencecontribution.
conference#Chair: The chair of a trackworkshop is the child of a committee member and a parent of a trackworkshopchair.
conference#Track: The track is a child of conferencepart which is the parent of workshop.
conference#Workshop: The workshop is the child of conferencepart which is the parent of track.
conference#Tutorial: The tutorial is part of the conferencepart which is the parent of the workshop.
conference#Rejected_contribution: The rejectedcontribution is the child of the reviewedcontribution which is the parent of the camerareadycontribution.
conference#Reviewed_contribution: The submittedcontribution is the parent of the acceptedcontribution and the camerareadycontribution. The writtencontribution is the child of the regularcontribution and the reviewedcontribution is the parent of the rejectedcontribution.
conference#Review: The conferencedocument is the parent of conferenceannouncement and is the child of conferencedocument.
conference#Late_paid_applicant: The latepaidapplicant is equivalent to the paidapplicant which is a child of the registeeredapplicant.
conference#Paid_applicant: The paid applicant is the parent of the latepaid and earlypaid applicants. The registeered and conference applicants are both children of the paid applicant.
conference#Early_paid_applicant: The earlypaidapplicant is a child of the paidapplicant, the registeeredapplicant is a child of the conferenceapplicant and the conferenceapplicant is a child of a person.
conference#Organizer: The organizer is a child of a committee member and a parent of a trackworkshopchair. He is also a child of Thing.
conference#Call_for_participation: callforparticipation is a child of conferencedocument which is parented by conferencewww.
conference#Registeered_applicant: The registeeredapplicant is the parent of the paidapplicant which is equivalent to the latepaidapplicant. The conferenceparticipant is the parent of the activeconferenceparticipant and the invitedspeaker is the child of the conferencecontributor.
conference#Track-workshop_chair: The trackworkshopchair is the child of the person who is the parent of the reviewer.
conference#Conference_www: conferencewww is the child of conferencedocument which is the parent of callforpaper.
conference#Review_preference: reviewpreference is a child of Thing.
